{"id":2040,"date":"2025-02-28T09:03:00","date_gmt":"2025-02-28T09:03:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/?p=2040"},"modified":"2026-02-15T02:26:22","modified_gmt":"2026-02-15T02:26:22","slug":"why-we-need-to-start-moving-offline","status":"publish","type":"blog","link":"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/blog\/why-we-need-to-start-moving-offline\/","title":{"rendered":"Why we need to start moving offline\u00a0"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-post\" data-elementor-id=\"2040\" class=\"elementor elementor-2040\" data-elementor-post-type=\"blog\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-74d7ce25 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"74d7ce25\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" id=\"sub-page-hero-banner\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-59bd4583 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-child\" data-id=\"59bd4583\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-476f0e4e page-title elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"476f0e4e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Why we need to start moving offline\u00a0<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5c10fa5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"5c10fa5\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tWritten by Ruvimbo Kuuzabuwe \u2014 February 28, 2025\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2076d304 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"2076d304\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-668f9fb elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"668f9fb\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>You may have noticed we\u2019ve been quieter than usual online. The reason is we\u2019re fortifying our communication strategy.\u00a0<\/p><p>Across Europe, we are seeing a seismic shift in politics veering towards the right. The far-right have been emboldened to take away our freedoms. In these current times, we need to rally and find ways of communicating and building power outside of social media platforms.<\/p><p>While billionaires fund political campaigns, platforms actively censor ads that challenge the status quo. They claim to connect us, yet they silence critical conversations about the very social issues that shape our lives.<\/p><p>This isn\u2019t just about algorithms, it\u2019s about power. Whose stories are heard, and whose are erased?<\/p><p>By joining our mailing list, you\u2019re fighting against the noise of biased platforms. Stay informed, stay empowered, and stay connected to the conversations they don\u2019t want you to hear.\u00a0<\/p><p>The Level Up community is at the heart of the work we do.<\/p><p>Without you, we would not have been able to send messages of solidarity to Kathryn Mayorga \u2013 or over 1,000 messages of solidarity to the mothers whose babies died in prison.\u00a0<\/p><p>Without you, we wouldn\u2019t have been able to bombard L\u2019Oreal executives with more than 700 demands to release the product testing information for cancerous Black hair products.<\/p><p>Without you, we wouldn\u2019t have been able to push the press regulator to implement the UK\u2019s first guidelines on reporting fatal domestic abuse \u2013 or been able to change countless victim-blaming headlines by creating mass complaints to newspapers.<\/p><p>Without you, we wouldn\u2019t have been able to hold the biggest baby protest in history to call for an end to the imprisonment of pregnant women and mothers. And without that, Eastenders and Coronation Street would never have put pregnancy in prison in the spotlight.\u00a0<\/p><p>Without you, we wouldn\u2019t have trained over 400 of you to intervene when it comes to police harassment.\u00a0<\/p><p>And none of this action took place on social media.<\/p><p>So stay connected with us.\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/levelup.yourmovement.org\/p\/join-us\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Join our mailing list<\/a>, come to our trainings.\u00a0<\/p><p>Source:<\/p><p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.theguardian.com\/us-news\/2025\/jan\/20\/trump-inauguration-tech-executives\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https:\/\/www.theguardian.com\/us-news\/2025\/jan\/20\/trump-inauguration-tech-executives<\/a><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"featured_media":2042,"template":"","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"give_campaign_id":0},"class_list":["post-2040","blog","type-blog","status-publish","has-post-thumbnail","hentry"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/blog\/2040","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/blog"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/blog"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/2042"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2040"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}